When a deviation file is having a branch unsupported, followed by leaf of it.
here branch is subcomponent and the leaf after it is name.

When the branch is cut while processing - it deviates the whole.
After that when the leaf is attempted - it throws error "node not found".
This may be better handled.

**deviation file (report_bug.yang):**
_module report_bug {

